Initial
1. Create your project folder. npm init, git init, and make a .gitignore file.
2. .gitignore file
  node_modules
  bundle.js
  bundle.js.map

Root
1. setup .babelrc
2. setup webpack.config.js

Client Folder
1. index.js (entry point for browser)
2. install react, react-dom

Public Folder
1. index.html (that will be served to browser)
2. bundle.js - lives here (set up on webpack.config.js)

Server Folder
1. set up index.js.
2. Express
3. Morgan - logging middleware
4. static file-serving middleware
5. body-parser - body parsing middleware
6. api routes
7. 404 error handler
8. send index.html
9. error 500 handler
10. port listener
